- Replicate Account: [https://replicate.com/](https://replicate.com/)
    

### Usage

1. Create a fork
2. Update collection variables
3. Send requests

- Models: [https://replicate.com/explore?utm_source=dashboard-models](https://replicate.com/explore?utm_source=dashboard-models)
    

### Models

50+ models, including Llama (by Meta AI, open-weight) and Mixtral (by Mistral AI, open-weight).
